<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MyBusiness - اربح المكافآت</title>
    <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Tahoma', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #0D1117;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #161b22, #0D1117);
            border-radius: 24px;
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .logo {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            background: #CDF0B4;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #CDF0B4, #a8d8ea);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        p {
            color: #8b949e;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #CDF0B4;
            color: #0D1117;
            padding: 14px 40px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(205, 240, 180, 0.3);
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .feature {
            background: #161b22;
            padding: 16px 8px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #8b949e;
        }
        .feature span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 24px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #484f58;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">💰</div>
        <h1>MyBusiness</h1>
        <p>اربح مكافآت حقيقية من خلال مشاهدة إعلانات الفيديو القصيرة. اجمع العملات والجواهر والنقاط، وحوّلها إلى هدايا وجوائز!</p>
        
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <span>🪙</span>
                عملات
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <span>💎</span>
                جواهر
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <span>🎁</span>
                جوائز
            </div>
        </div>

        <a href="#" class="btn">ابدأ الآن</a>
        <div class="footer">© 2026 MyBusiness - جميع الحقوق محفوظة</div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // تسجيل Service Worker
        if ('serviceWorker' in navigator) {
            navigator.serviceWorker.register('/sw.js')
                .then(() => console.log('✅ Service Worker registered successfully!'))
                .catch((err) => console.log('❌ Service Worker registration failed:', err));
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
